<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error - Page Not Found</title>


    <style>
        body{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            background: #f3f6fb;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }

        .box{
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 60px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        h1{
            font-size: 60px;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #d9534f;  /* beautiful red tone */
        }

        h2{
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        p{
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-top: 8px;
            opacity: .8;
        }

        a{
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background: #0275d8;
            padding: 12px 22px;
            display: inline-block;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: 0.25s;
        }

        a:hover{
            background: #025aa5;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="box">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Oops! Page Not Found</h2>
        <p>The page you're trying to access doesn't exist or may have been moved.</p>
        <a href="/">â¬… Go Back to Login</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
